    <deploymentStatus>Deployed</deploymentStatus>
    <deprecated>false</deprecated>
    <description>Junction object for the many to many association of the program to the product. Single program can be assigned to multiple products under same brand or vise versa - A single product can have multiple programs associated to it.</description>
